Each of these platforms has its own area

65
00:02:47.002 --> 00:02:48.007
in which they excel.

66
00:02:48.007 --> 00:02:50.007
Quill focuses more on readability

67
00:02:50.007 --> 00:02:52.005
while the other two products try to focus more

68
